John Lewis believed "each generation must do its part to create an even more fair, more just society."

@HouseDemocrats just did our part and passed the Freedom to Vote: John R. Lewis Act.

It's time for the Senate to do the same and ensure every American's voice can be heard.

From creating millions of new jobs to addressing our outdated infrastructure, the Infrastructure Investment and Jobs Act is huge for our nation.
 
@SecretaryPete and I discuss this unprecedented investment on the latest episode of the Clyburn Chronicles.
https://t.co/rSjTO3s7l0

You can’t access vital telehealth without reliable, high-speed broadband.
 
Children need it to receive an equitable education, and businesses can’t operate without it.
 
@POTUS’ bipartisan Infrastructure Investment and Jobs Act will bring rural communities into the 21st century.

If you think this month's jobs report is strong, just wait until we start adding millions of jobs thanks to the #BuildBackBetter Act &amp; the bipartisan Infrastructure Investment and Jobs Act.

@POTUS &amp; Democrats are building America's economy back better.
https://t.co/XKpuMJTRx6

The COVID-19 pandemic has been an existential threat to small businesses. 
 
@HouseDemocrats have worked alongside @POTUS to pass policies like the #AmericanRescuePlan, helping millions stay afloat.
 
This #SmallBusinessWeek we ought to continue our promise to #buildbackbetter.

Today, Republicans at every level of government are leading the assault on the right to vote. We can’t wait on bipartisan support to protect it.

@RepMondaire and I agree: we need a constitutional rights exception to the filibuster.
